---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Thunder Bay CRM systems | ThunderBayAI" description="CRM systems for Thunder Bay businesses that need better lead tracking, follow-up, pipeline visibility, and conversion workflows.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Primary keyword: Thunder Bay CRM systems</p>
      <h1>Thunder Bay CRM systems that improve lead tracking, follow-up, and close rate.</h1>
      <p class="lead">A CRM should not just store contacts. It should move leads forward, support fast response, trigger follow-up, and help owners see where deals are getting stuck.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button" href="https://frayze.ca/solutions/crm-automation/">See the Frayze Automation System</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/ai-opportunity-audit">Get a Free AI Opportunity Audit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container grid grid-2">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>What a strong CRM system should handle</h2>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>capture leads from calls, forms, text, and ads</li>
          <li>assign and tag opportunities correctly</li>
          <li>trigger follow-up sequences automatically</li>
          <li>track quote, booking, and close stages</li>
          <li>show where the pipeline is leaking</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2>When the current setup is not enough</h2>
        <p class="muted">If leads live in inboxes, text threads, notebooks, or multiple disconnected tools, the business is running blind. That usually means lost revenue even before more traffic is added.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Related pathways</h2>
      <div class="kicker-bar">
        <a class="kicker-chip" href="/thunder-bay-ai-automation">Thunder Bay AI automation</a>
        <a class="kicker-chip" href="/thunder-bay-lead-generation-systems">Lead generation systems</a>
        <a class="kicker-chip" href="/contractor-crm-automation-thunder-bay">Contractor CRM automation</a>
        <a class="kicker-chip" href="/website-audit-thunder-bay">Website audit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
